				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\frac{{j}_{light}}{{j}_{dark}}$$\end{document}  for the film was approximately 33, and the photocurrent value of 1.9 mA cm−2 is amongst the highest values reported in the literature for CuO47.Figure 6
